3309Nahetuyā pañca, naārammaṇe tīṇi, naadhipatiyā pañca…pe…  nakamme pañca, navipāke pañca, naāhāre tīṇi, naindriye tīṇi, najhāne pañca, namagge pañca, nasampayutte tīṇi, navippayutte tīṇi, nonatthiyā tīṇi, novigate tīṇi.
